#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn8.6"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn8.6:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 8 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 8 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn8.6:0.2"
msgid "1. Vaṅgīsavagga "
msgstr "1. With Vaṅgīsa "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 6. Sāriputtasutta → sārīputtasuttaṃ (s3)
msgctxt "sn8.6:0.3"
msgid "6. Sāriputtasutta "
msgstr "6. With Sāriputta "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts1ed1.190, pts2ed1.409, sc1
msgctxt "sn8.6:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ āyasmā sāriputto sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. "
msgstr "At one time Venerable Sāriputta was staying near Sāvatthī in Jeta’s Grove, Anāthapiṇḍika’s monastery. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. VAR: anelagalāya → aneḷagalāya (bj, pts2, mr) | anelagaḷāya (s1-3, km, pts1)
msgctxt "sn8.6:1.2"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena āyasmā sāriputto bhikkhū dhammiyā kathāya sandasseti samādapeti samuttejeti sampahaṃseti poriyā vācāya vissaṭṭhāya anelagalāya atthassa viññāpaniyā. "
msgstr "Now at that time Venerable Sāriputta was educating, encouraging, firing up, and inspiring the mendicants in the assembly hall with a Dhamma talk. His words were polished, clear, articulate, and expressed the meaning. "

msgctxt "sn8.6:1.3"
msgid "Te ca bhikkhū aṭṭhiṃ katvā manasi katvā sabbacetasā samannāharitvā ohitasotā dhammaṃ suṇanti. "
msgstr "And those mendicants were paying heed, paying attention, engaging wholeheartedly, and lending an ear. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn8.6:1.4"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmato vaṅgīsassa etadahosi: "
msgstr "Then Venerable Vaṅgīsa thought, "

msgctxt "sn8.6:1.5"
msgid "“ayaṃ kho āyasmā sāriputto bhikkhū dhammiyā kathāya sandasseti samādapeti samuttejeti sampahaṃseti poriyā vācāya vissaṭṭhāya anelagalāya atthassa viññāpaniyā. "
msgstr "“This Venerable Sāriputta is educating the mendicants. … "

msgctxt "sn8.6:1.6"
msgid "Te ca bhikkhū aṭṭhiṃ katvā manasi katvā sabbacetasā samannāharitvā ohitasotā dhammaṃ suṇanti. "
msgstr "And those mendicants are paying heed, paying attention, engaging wholeheartedly, and lending an ear. "

msgctxt "sn8.6:1.7"
msgid "Yannūnāhaṃ āyasmantaṃ sāriputtaṃ sammukhā sāruppāhi gāthāhi abhitthaveyyan”ti. "
msgstr "Why don’t I extoll him in his presence with fitting verses?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn8.6:2.1"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā vaṅgīso uṭṭhāyāsanā ekaṃsaṃ uttarāsaṅgaṃ karitvā yenāyasmā sāriputto tenañjaliṃ paṇāmetvā āyasmantaṃ sāriputtaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then Venerable Vaṅgīsa got up from his seat, arranged his robe over one shoulder, raised his joined palms toward Sāriputta, and said, "

msgctxt "sn8.6:2.2"
msgid "“paṭibhāti maṃ, āvuso sāriputta, paṭibhāti maṃ, āvuso sāriputtā”ti. "
msgstr "“I feel inspired to speak, Reverend Sāriputta! I feel inspired to speak, Reverend Sāriputta!” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn8.6:2.3"
msgid "“Paṭibhātu taṃ, āvuso vaṅgīsā”ti. "
msgstr "“Then speak as you feel inspired,” said Sāriputta. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn8.6:2.4"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā vaṅgīso āyasmantaṃ sāriputtaṃ sammukhā sāruppāhi gāthāhi abhitthavi: "
msgstr "Then Vaṅgīsa extolled Sāriputta in his presence with fitting verses: "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn8.6:3.1"
msgid "“Gambhīrapañño medhāvī, "
msgstr "“Deep in wisdom, intelligent, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn8.6:3.2"
msgid "maggāmaggassa kovido; "
msgstr "expert in the variety of paths; "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn8.6:3.3"
msgid "Sāriputto mahāpañño, "
msgstr "Sāriputta, so greatly wise, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn8.6:3.4"
msgid "dhammaṃ deseti bhikkhunaṃ. "
msgstr "teaches Dhamma to the mendicants. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts2ed1.410, sc4
msgctxt "sn8.6:4.1"
msgid "Saṃkhittenapi deseti, "
msgstr "He teaches in brief, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn8.6:4.2"
msgid "vitthārenapi bhāsati; "
msgstr "or he speaks at length. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn8.6:4.3"
msgid "Sāḷikāyiva nigghoso, "
msgstr "His call, like a myna bird, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn8.6:4.4"
msgid "paṭibhānaṃ udīrayi. "
msgstr "overflows with inspiration. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "sn8.6:5.1"
msgid "Tassa taṃ desayantassa, "
msgstr "While he teaches "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn8.6:5.2"
msgid "suṇanti madhuraṃ giraṃ; "
msgstr "the mendicants listen to his sweet voice, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn8.6:5.3"
msgid "Sarena rajanīyena, "
msgstr "sounding attractive, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn8.6:5.4"
msgid "savanīyena vaggunā; "
msgstr "clear and graceful. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn8.6:5.5"
msgid "Udaggacittā muditā, "
msgstr "They listen joyfully, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn8.6:5.6"
msgid "sotaṃ odhenti bhikkhavo”ti. "
msgstr "their hearts uplifted.”"

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
